metadata.name: ActivityPub::ProcessAccountService when account is not suspended queues suspension worker

sql_query.sql: SELECT "domain_blocks".* FROM "domain_blocks" WHERE "domain_blocks"."domain" IN ($1, $2) ORDER BY char_length(domain) desc LIMIT $3
